MyNutrition offers the user a complete control of his nutritional values, with attractive features like storing lot of information about your meals, including name, description, nutritional values and even where it was consumed, and allowing you to track all nutritional needs based on basic personal information like your height, weight, gender or exercise level.
The main goal of MyNutrition is recommend you what you should eat to keep with and healthy and solve the problem of not remembering what you have eaten this afternoon.
